ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 17th day of November, 2015, the Application for an Exercise of King’s Bench Power or Extraordinary Jurisdiction is DENIED, and the Application to Substitute Corrected and Updated Affidavit is DISMISSED AS MOOT.
